<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>STEM | 차세대 글로벌 AI 에듀테크 및 초밀착 입시 매니지먼트 플랫폼</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0A1931;       
            --secondary: #15305B;     
            --accent: #00E5FF;        
            --accent-hover: #00B8D4;
            --text-main: #1E293B;     
            --text-muted: #64748B;    
            --bg-light: #F8FAFC;      
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --border: #E2E8F0;
            --cafe-main: #03C75A;
            --card-shadow: 0 20px 40px -15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: "Pretendard Variable", Pretendard, sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--white); color: var(--text-main); line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }

        /* GNB 구조 고도화 및 하위메뉴 깨짐 방지 */
        header {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); z-index: 2000;
        }
        .nav-container { max-width: 1440px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; height: 80px; position: relative; }
        .logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primary); letter-spacing: -1.5px; cursor: pointer; }
        .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
        
        nav { height: 100%; }
        nav > ul { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 0.5rem; height: 100%; align-items: center; }
        nav > ul > li { position: relative; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; }
        
        nav > ul > li > a { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-main); padding: 0 1.2rem; cursor: pointer; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none; transition: var(--transition); }
        nav > ul > li:hover > a, nav > ul > li > a.active { color: #00A3B8; }
        
        /* 드롭다운 메뉴 스타일 초기화 및 절대좌표 고정 (디자인 깨짐 수정) */
        .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute; top: 80px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); width: 240px; display: none; list-style: none; padding: 0.8rem 0; z-index: 2100;
        }
        .dropdown-menu li { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
        .dropdown-menu li a { padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-main); text-decoration: none; display: block; font-weight: 600; transition: var(--transition); cursor: pointer; text-align: left; }
        .dropdown-menu li a:hover { background-color: var(--bg-light); color: #00A3B8; padding-left: 1.8rem; }
        nav > ul > li:hover .dropdown-menu { display: block; }

        .cta-btn-fixed {
            background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--white); padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: var(--transition); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(10, 25, 49, 0.15);
        }
        .cta-btn-fixed:hover { background-color: #11274c; transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--accent); }

        .page-content { display: none; padding-top: 80px; animation: pageFadeIn 0.35s ease-out; }
        .page-content.active { display: block; }
        @keyframes pageFadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

        section { padding: 6.5rem 2rem; }
        .section-inner { max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .center-title-wrap { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
        .section-tag { display: inline-block; background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.08); color: #00A3B8; padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .section-title { font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); letter-spacing: -1.5px; line-height: 1.3; }
        .section-subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 850px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

        /* [HOME] */
        .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1931 0%, #15305B 100%); color: var(--white); padding: 12rem 2rem 10rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 4.4rem; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
        .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.35rem; color: #94A3B8; max-width: 950px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto; line-height: 1.8; }
        .hero .btn-main { background-color: transparent; color: var(--white); padding: 1.2rem 3.2rem; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.2); transition: var(--transition); cursor: pointer; }
        .hero .btn-main:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); background-color: var(--accent); color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.4); }

        .stats-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2.5rem; text-align: center; margin-top: -4rem; position: relative; z-index: 10; padding: 0 2rem; max-width: 1340px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        .stat-card { background: var(--white); padding: 3rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border: 1px solid #F1F5F9; }
        .stat-card h2 { font-size: 3.6rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .stat-card h2 span { color: #00A3B8; }
        .stat-card p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-main); font-weight: 700; }

        .home-grid-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; margin-top: 6rem; align-items: center; }
        .home-corporate-timeline { list-style: none; }
        .home-corporate-timeline li { position: relative; padding-left: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
        .home-corporate-timeline li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.5rem; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
        .home-corporate-timeline li::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 5px; top: 1.5rem; width: 2.5px; height: 100%; background: var(--border); }
        .home-corporate-timeline li:last-child::after { display: none; }
        .home-corporate-timeline li h4 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .home-corporate-timeline li p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.98rem; line-height: 1.6; }

        /* [BUSINESS MODEL] */
        .ubion-style-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
        .ubion-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; transition: var(--transition); display: flex; flex-direction: column; scroll-margin-top: 100px; }
        .ubion-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
        .ubion-card-img-holder { background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--accent); height: 180px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 900; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .ubion-card-img-holder::after { content: ''; position: absolute; width: 150%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent); top: 0; left: -150%; transition: 0.6s; }
        .ubion-card:hover .ubion-card-img-holder::after { left: 150%; }
        .ubion-card-body { padding: 2rem; flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
        .ubion-card-body h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .ubion-card-body p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        .ubion-sub-links { list-style: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; }
        .ubion-sub-links li { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
        .ubion-sub-links li::before { content: '▶'; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #00A3B8; }

        /* [ABOUT STEM] */
        .about-vision-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2.5rem; margin-top: 4rem; }
        .vision-card { background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 4rem 3rem; border-radius: 20px; border-top: 5px solid var(--accent); }
        .vision-card.light { background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-main); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 5px solid var(--primary); }
        .vision-card h3 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; }
        
        /* [PROGRAMS] */
        .program-7-container { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2.5rem; }
        .prog-row-item { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 2.5fr 4fr 1.5fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; transition: var(--transition); }
        .prog-row-item:hover { border-color: #00E5FF; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
        .prog-badge-num { width: 60px; height: 60px; background: var(--bg-light); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primary); border: 2px solid var(--border); }
        .prog-row-item:hover .prog-badge-num { background: var(--primary); color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--primary); }
        .prog-meta-title h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .prog-meta-title span { font-size: 0.85rem; background: #EEF2F6; color: #475569; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.2rem; }
        .prog-desc-text { font-size: 0.98rem; color: #334155; line-height: 1.7; }
        .prog-desc-text ul { list-style: none; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        .prog-desc-text ul li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .prog-target-time { font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: right; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; }

        /* [FACULTY & STRATEGY] */
        .faculty-main-wrapper { scroll-margin-top: 100px; }
        .faculty-main-wrapper h3 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary); display: inline-block; }
        .inst-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 3rem; margin-bottom: 6rem; }
        .inst-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
        .inst-img { background: #E2E8F0; width: 35%; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center; }
        .inst-img svg { width: 90%; fill: #475569; }
        .inst-desc { padding: 2.5rem; width: 65%; }
        .inst-desc h4 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .inst-desc .bio { list-style: none; font-size: 0.95rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; }
        .inst-desc .bio li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #334155; }

        /* [NOTICES] */
        .cafe-board-container { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
        .cafe-board-header { background-color: #FAFAFA; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.2rem 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--cafe-main); }
        .cafe-list-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .cafe-list-table th, .cafe-list-table td { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F1F5F9; text-align: center; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .cafe-list-table th { background-color: #FAFAFA; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-muted); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .cafe-title-td { text-align: left !important; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; color: #333; }
        .cafe-title-td:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: var(--cafe-main); }
        .cafe-badge-notice { background-color: #FFECEF; color: #FF4D6A; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; margin-right: 0.5rem; }
        .comment-count-badge { color: var(--cafe-main); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-left: 0.3rem; }

        .cafe-detail-view { display: none; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
        .cafe-detail-back-btn { background: #F1F5F9; color: var(--text-main); padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; border: none; cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .cafe-article-header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .cafe-article-body { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.9; min-height: 200px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 3rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: justify; }
        
        .comment-list { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .comment-item { padding: 1.2rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #F1F5F9; position: relative; }
        .comment-meta { font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .comment-writer { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-main); margin-right: 1rem; }
        .comment-date { color: var(--text-muted); }
        .comment-delete-btn { position: absolute; right: 0; top: 1.2rem; background: transparent; color: #FF4D6A; border: none; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }
        .comment-form-box { background: #FAFAFA; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.2rem; }
        .comment-textarea { width: 100%; height: 80px; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; resize: none; }
        .comment-submit-btn { background-color: var(--cafe-main); color: white; border: none; padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 800; cursor: pointer; float: right; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

        /* [SUPPORT FAQ] */
        .support-wrapper { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .faq-item { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; overflow: hidden; background: var(--white); box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
        .faq-q { padding: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .faq-a { background: var(--bg-light); padding: 1.8rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: none; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; }

        /* [APPLY FORM] */
        .form-page-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); padding: 4.5rem 3.5rem; }
        .form-section-title { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-left: 0.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); }
        .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .form-group.fullwidth { grid-column: span 2; }
        .form-group label { display: block; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: var(--primary); font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .form-group label span { color: #FF4D6A; margin-left: 0.2rem; }
        .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea { width: 100%; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; background-color: var(--bg-light); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-main); transition: var(--transition); }
        .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { background-color: var(--white); border-color: #00A3B8; outline: none; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 163, 184, 0.1); }
        
        .phone-input-wrapper { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; }
        .phone-input-wrapper select { width: 110px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        
        .checkbox-agreement-box { background: var(--bg-light); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.8rem; }
        .checkbox-agreement-box input[type="checkbox"] { width: 18px; height: 18px; margin-top: 0.2rem; cursor: pointer; }
        .checkbox-agreement-box label { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #475569; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; line-height: 1.5; }

        .btn-submit-direct { width: 100%; background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--white); padding: 1.3rem; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; border: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: var(--transition); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(10, 25, 49, 0.15); }
        .btn-submit-direct:hover { background-color: #11274c; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.25); }

        footer { background-color: #1E293B; color: #94A3B8; padding: 4rem 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; border-top: 1px solid #334155; }
        .footer-inner { max-width: 1440px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; }

        @media (max-width: 1100px) {
            .nav-container nav, .cta-btn-fixed { display: none; }
            .stats-container, .ubion-style-container, .about-vision-grid, .inst-grid, .prog-row-item, .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .form-group.fullwidth { grid-column: span 1; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div onclick="navigateTo('home')" class="logo">STEM<span>.</span></div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a id="nav-home" onclick="navigateTo('home')" class="active">홈</a></li>
                    <li>
                        <a id="nav-bm" onclick="navigateTo('bm')">사업 영역</a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('bm', 'b2c')">B2C 프리미엄 교육</a></li>
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('bm', 'b2b')">B2B 기업 역량 교육</a></li>
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('bm', 'b2g')">B2G 공공 에듀테크</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a id="nav-about" onclick="navigateTo('about')">STEM 신념</a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('about')">교육 철학 및 비전</a></li>
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('about')">핵심 가치 매트릭스</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><a id="nav-programs" onclick="navigateTo('programs')">교육 커리큘럼</a></li>
                    <li>
                        <a id="nav-faculty" onclick="navigateTo('faculty')">교수진 & 연구원</a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('faculty', 'teacher')">대치 대표 강사진</a></li>
                            <li><a onclick="navigateTo('faculty', 'strategy')">입시 데이터 전략팀</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><a id="nav-notices" onclick="navigateTo('notices')">학습 공지 라운지</a></li>
                    <li><a id="nav-support" onclick="navigateTo('support')">고객지원 FAQ</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <button onclick="navigateTo('apply')" class="cta-btn-fixed">무료 진단 신청</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div id="page-home" class="page-content active">
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <span class="section-tag" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color:var(--accent);">GLOBAL EDUTECH STANDARD</span>
                <h1>단순 주입을 넘어 생각의 회로를 혁신하다<br>성과를 계량화하는 <span>지능형 플랫폼 STEM</span></h1>
                <p>최상위 0.1%의 수학적·인과적 직관 모델을 AI 데이터 아키텍처로 구현하여 이식합니다. 일방통행식 판서 강의의 명확한 한계를 극복하고 실시간으로 학습 구멍을 추적해 완전무결한 성과 매트릭스를 증명합니다.</p>
                <button onclick="navigateTo('apply')" class="btn-main">실시간 1:1 두뇌 메타인지 무료 진단 코스 신청 ➔</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-card"><h2>94.2<span>%</span></h2><p>재원생 평균 성적 대폭 향상</p></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><h2>2,140<span>명</span></h2><p>의치한수·SKY 누적 합격생</p></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><h2>98.8<span>%</span></h2><p>학부모 실시간 만족 피드백</p></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><h2>0<span>%</span></h2><p>단순 변형오답 제로 지향</p></div>
        </div>

        <section>
            <div class="section-inner">
